$interpreted: Charle: Repeat what you just said!
Tica: I-I'm really sorry. I didn't maintain a neutral position and I went to fight for the princess. Forgive me...
Charle: I will scold you about that later! The things about Elio you just mentioned, tell me again!
Tica: Well, on the battlefield, wings suddenly popped out from his back. He then rescued Theodore and took him away!
Tica: He even referred to Theodore as "father"!
Tica: Headmaster Ceres? I'll...umm...take my leave now...is that ok with you?
Charle: ...Elio is a member of the Feather Clan? And he is Theodore's son?
Charle: Why didn't he tell me about these things?
Charle: When did he find out about all this?
Tica: Headmaster, I'm REALLY going to leave now...kay?
Tica: Oh, by the way, I accidentally blew up a pot in the cafeteria a while ago. I'm sure you'll forgive me for that too, right?
Charle: If had only I cared about him more...
